quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  28,36,"Nuko Musa abagejejeho ibitangaza byacu bigaragara, baravuga bati \"Ibi nta kindi biricyo uretse ko ari uburozi bw’ubuhimbano, kandi ibi (uduhamagarira) ntitwigeze tubyumva ku babyeyi bacu bo hambere"
  28,37,"Musa aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye ni we uzi neza uwazanye umuyoboro umuturutseho, kandi ni na we uzi uzagira iherezo ryiza ku munsi w’imperuka. Mu by’ukuri, inkozi z’ibibi ntizizatsinda"
  28,38,"Nuko Farawo aravuga ati \"Yemwe banyacyubahiro! Nta yindi mana nzi mufite itari njye, bityo ntwikira amatafari yewe Hamana, maze unyubakire umunara muremure kugira ngo nshobore kubona Imana ya Musa. Kuko mu by’ukuri, nkeka ko (Musa) ari umwe mu banyabinyoma"
  28,39,Maze (Farawo) n’ingabo ze bigira abibone mu gihugu bitari mu kuri kandi banibwira ko batazagarurwa iwacu (kwa Allah)
  28,40,"Nuko tumufatana n’ingabo ze maze tubajugunya mu nyanja. Bityo, reba uko iherezo ry’inkozi z’ibibi ryagenze"
  28,41,"Twanabagize abayobozi bahamagarira (abantu) kugana umuriro, kandi ku munsi w’imperuka ntibazarokorwa"
  28,42,"Twanabakurikije umuvumo hano ku isi, ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka bazaba bari mu bantu babi"
  28,43,"Kandi rwose twahaye Musa igitabo (Tawurati) nyuma yo kurimbura ibisekuru byo hambere, (ngo kibe) urumuri n’umuyoboro ndetse n’impuhwe ku bantu, kugira ngo babashe kwibuka"